4Geeks Academy offers a course in Applied Artificial Intelligence. This course is designed for professionals looking to leverage AI in their current roles. It covers various topics such as generative AI, context, prompts, and models. The course duration is 6 weeks, with 2 live, online classes per week. The class size is limited to 12 people. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. No previous experience is required. For more information, visit [this website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop